      <title>中国召开年度经济会议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-11/china-begins-annual-economic-meeting-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国即将召开年度经济工作会议，制定明年的政策，高层领导人暗示，在与美国爆发贸易战的威胁下，将采取更有力的刺激措施。彭博社的 Stephen Engle 将为您报道这一预期。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-11/china-begins-annual-economic-meeting-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 00:58:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登计划正式阻止美国向新日铁出售钢铁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-11/biden-plans-to-formally-block-sale-to-nippon-steel-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社透露，一旦本月晚些时候交易被交回给拜登，总统乔·拜登计划以国家安全为由正式阻止美国钢铁公司以 141 亿美元的价格出售给新日铁。彭博社的 Josh Wingrove 在“彭博：亚洲贸易”中报道了这一独家新闻。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-11/biden-plans-to-formally-block-sale-to-nippon-steel-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 00:55:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黄金价格上涨，因交易员预测美国通胀数据</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/gold-holds-advance-as-traders-count-down-to-us-inflation-figures</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易商为美国通胀数据做准备，黄金价格连续三天上涨，这将有助于确定美联储在下周的今年最后一次会议上是降息还是维持利率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/gold-holds-advance-as-traders-count-down-to-us-inflation-figures</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 00:39:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度创纪录的股市涨势在 2025 年面临更大障碍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/india-s-record-breaking-stock-run-faces-bigger-hurdles-in-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着企业盈利减弱以及全球基金对市场变得谨慎，印度股市前所未有的上涨势头可能在 2025 年遭遇阻碍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/india-s-record-breaking-stock-run-faces-bigger-hurdles-in-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 00:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲私募股权投资主管辞去加拿大养老金业务，转而前往阿布扎比担任全球职务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/asia-pe-chief-quits-canada-pension-for-global-role-in-abu-dhabi</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，加拿大养老金计划投资委员会的亚洲私募股权主管已离职，加盟阿布扎比养老基金，加入了在交易低迷之际离开香港的一大批香港交易人士的行列。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/asia-pe-chief-quits-canada-pension-for-global-role-in-abu-dhabi</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 00:15:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国通胀数据和 OPEC 市场报告公布前油价保持稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/latest-oil-market-news-and-analytics-for-dec-11</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国关键通胀数据和石油输出国组织月度报告公布之前，油价保持稳定，这些报告将提供市场概况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/latest-oil-market-news-and-analytics-for-dec-11</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 23:30:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲股市上涨，美元在美国 CPI 公布前走弱：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚洲股市小幅走高，交易员等待关键的美国通胀数据，以判断美联储下周是否会降息或维持利率。美元结束了连续三天的涨势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 22:29:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Voyix 称，NCR 拆分后，Atleos 被低估</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/engaged-capital-says-voyix-atleos-undervalued-after-ncr-breakup</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Engaged Capital 认为，如果市场没有开始正确评估这些业务，那么从 NCR Corp 中分离出来的 NCR Atleos Corp. 和 NCR Voyix Corp. 可能会吸引金融或战略买家的收购兴趣，这位激进投资者在周二的彭博激进主义论坛 2024 上表示。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/engaged-capital-says-voyix-atleos-undervalued-after-ncr-breakup</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 17:58:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
